<subSubSection id="8895FBE6BB2BFF9EFF00F87AD9C175B0" lastPageId="8" lastPageNumber="53" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="C030A86DBB2BFF91FF00F87ADDDD7D41" blockId="7.[136,1452,1921,2092]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FF00F87AD94672D2" bold="true" box="[189,304,1957,1983]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">Diagnosis</emphasis>
:—Plants of 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB2BFF91FE7BF87ADADD72D2" box="[454,683,1957,1983]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" isHybrid="true" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="trageri">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FE7BF87ADADD72D2" box="[454,683,1957,1983]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">Kalanchoe ×trageri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differ from the floury waxy 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB2BFF91FBB8F879DC0E72D2" authorityName="Baker" authorityYear="1883" box="[1029,1144,1957,1983]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pumila">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FBB8F879DC0E72D2" box="[1029,1144,1957,1983]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">K. pumila</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, one of its parents, by all plant parts being smooth and virtually non-waxy, as is found in 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB2BFF91FCD9F815DC6D728E" authorityName="Von Poellnitz" authorityYear="1934" box="[868,1051,1993,2019]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blossfeldiana">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FCD9F815DC6D728E" box="[868,1051,1993,2019]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">K. blossfeldiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the other parent. Leaf shape of 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB2BFF91FA2FF815D8907D6A" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" isHybrid="true" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="trageri">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FA2FF815DDD3728E" box="[1426,1445,1994,2019]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">K</emphasis>
. × 
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FF25F831D8907D6A" box="[152,230,2030,2055]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">trageri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is intermediate between that of 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB2BFF91FDF4F831DA887D6A" authorityName="Von Poellnitz" authorityYear="1934" box="[585,766,2029,2055]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blossfeldiana">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FDF4F831DA887D6A" box="[585,766,2029,2055]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">K. blossfeldiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB2BFF91FC8EF831DBD77D6A" authorityName="Baker" authorityYear="1883" box="[819,929,2029,2055]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pumila">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FC8EF831DBD77D6A" box="[819,929,2029,2055]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">K. pumila</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The adaxial surfaces of the corolla lobes of 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB2BFF91FA2FF831D96B7D46" authorityName="Von Poellnitz" authorityYear="1934" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blossfeldiana">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FA2FF831D96B7D46" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">K. blossfeldiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are crimson red and those of 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB2BFF91FDD5F7CDDAA17D46" authorityName="Baker" authorityYear="1883" box="[616,727,2065,2091]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pumila">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FDD5F7CDDAA17D46" box="[616,727,2065,2091]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">K. pumila</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
variously light to dark pink and purple-veined, while those of 
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB2BFF91FA2FF7CDDDD37D46" box="[1426,1445,2066,2091]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">K</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C030A86DBB24FF9EFF35FF40D9C175B0" blockId="8.[136,1451,158,221]" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB24FF9EFF35FF40D89075D5" box="[136,230,159,185]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" isHybrid="true" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="8" pageNumber="53" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="trageri">
× 
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB24FF9EFF25FF40D89075D5" box="[152,230,159,184]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">trageri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are bright dark reddish purple. In 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB24FF9EFDD8FF40DA9275D5" box="[613,740,159,185]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" isHybrid="true" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="8" pageNumber="53" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="trageri">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB24FF9EFDD8FF40DA0E75D5" box="[613,632,159,184]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">K</emphasis>
. × 
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB24FF9EFD2BFF40DA9275D5" box="[662,740,159,184]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">trageri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
the corolla lobes are distinctly recurved, as found in 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB24FF9EFA8BFF40DDD375D5" authorityName="Baker" authorityYear="1883" box="[1334,1445,158,184]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="8" pageNumber="53" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pumila">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB24FF9EFA8BFF40DDD375D5" box="[1334,1445,158,184]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">K. pumila</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but not in 
<taxonomicName id="078FD3EEBB24FF9EFF47FF1CD9C675B1" authorityName="Von Poellnitz" authorityYear="1934" box="[250,432,194,220]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="8" pageNumber="53" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="blossfeldiana">
<emphasis id="F2FB747FBB24FF9EFF47FF1CD9C675B1" box="[250,432,194,220]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">K. blossfeldiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
